Mary Phagan, Part 1,'' story by Larry McMurtry, NBC mini-series.
   _William Luce, ``The Woman He Loved,'' CBS Movie of the Week.
   _Norman Morrill, ``The Taking of Flight 847: The Uli Derickson
Story,'' NBC Movie of the Week.
   _Dennis Nemec, ``God Bless the Child,'' ABC Movie of the Week.
   _John Sacret Young, ``China Beach,'' ABC pilot.
