   _Jay Tarses, ``The `Slap' Maxwell Story, Part 1,'' ABC.
   Variety _ Musical, Award, Tribute, Special Event:
   _Jack Elinson, Jay Leno, Marvin Silbermintz, Jay Teitzell, Ted
Hermann, ``Jay Leno's Family Comedy Hour,'' NBC comedy-variety
special.
   _Jerry Juhl, ``A Muppet Family Christmas,'' ABC special.
   _Matt Neuman, Larry Arnstein, Steve Barker, Rich Hall, David
Hurwitz, Thomas Kramer, Elaine Pope, Lane Sarasohn, ``Not
Necessarily the News of the World,'' HBO comedy-variety special.
   _George Stevens Jr. and Jeffrey Lane, ``AFI Life Achievement
