<FIRST>r a PM-Lottery     03-03 0039</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Lottery,0044</SECOND>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
   Here are the winning weekly state lottery numbers picked Thursday:
</TEXT>
<NOTE>DELAWARE</NOTE>
<TEXT>
   Play 4: 0-4-2-2.
</TEXT>
