Charleston, S.C. 53 foggy; Cincinnati 36 cloudy; Cleveland 26
cloudy; Detroit 21 foggy; Miami 74 cloudy; New York 36 cloudy;
Philadelphia 33 partly cloudy; Pittsburgh 27 fair; Portland, Maine
20 partly cloudy; Washington 33 partly cloudy.
