59 foggy; Denver 24 freezing drizzle; Des Moines 22 freezing rain;
Indianapolis 36 cloudy; Kansas City 40 drizzle; Minneapolis-St. Paul
6 snow; Nashville 39 fair; St. Louis 45 cloudy.
