<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
   Here are the major business events and economic events scheduled
for the coming week (some dates are tentative; times are EST):
</TEXT>
<BYLINE>MONDAY, March 6</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
   
   KNOXVILLE, Tenn. _ Whittle Communication's ``Channel One''
premieres at Central High in Knoxville and five other schools across
the country.
