before speech to Economic Club.
</TEXT>
<BYLINE>TUESDAY, March 7</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
   
   WASHINGTON _ Labor Department reports on fourth quarter
productivity at 10 a.m.
   WASHINGTON _ The Federal Reserve Board reports on February
consumer credit.
   WASHINGTON _ The House Science Committee considers how to save
the Landsat earth-sensing satellite system facing a shutdown March
15 due to budget problems.
